---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SUPPORT_EMAIL } from "../../config/site";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Policy - Kafadar"
    description="Global privacy policy for Kafadar (GDPR, CCPA/CPRA, LGPD, KVKK aligned)."
>
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: February 17, 2026</p>

        <article class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-7">
            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">1. Data Controller</h2>
                <p>
                    Kafadar team is the data controller for the app and this website.
                    Contact:
                    <a
                        class="text-primary-600 hover:underline"
                        href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    2. Data We Collect
                </h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Account data (email, username, authentication identifiers).</li>
                    <li>
                        User content (created quizzes, answers, and shared results).
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Device and technical data (app version, device model, OS, error
                        logs, and technical network signals).
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Advertising and measurement data (such as advertising identifiers,
                        where legally permitted and consented).
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    3. Why We Process Data
                </h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>To provide core functionality (quiz creation and scoring).</li>
                    <li>To secure the service and prevent abuse.</li>
                    <li>To debug, maintain, and improve app performance.</li>
                    <li>To comply with legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    4. Legal Bases
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Depending on jurisdiction, we rely on contractual necessity, legitimate
                    interests, legal obligations, and where required, consent. This policy
                    is designed to support GDPR/UK GDPR, CCPA/CPRA, LGPD, and KVKK aligned
                    practices.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    5. Service Providers and Sharing
                </h2>
                <p>
                    We may share limited data with infrastructure and operational service
                    providers (for example, hosting/database/authentication and ad
                    services). We do not sell your personal information.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    6. International Transfers
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Data may be processed in countries other than your own. We aim to use
                    contractual and technical safeguards where required by law.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">7. Retention</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>
                        Account data is retained while your account is active and for a
                        limited period after deletion requests.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Certain records may be retained longer where required by law.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Verified deletion requests are processed as quickly as reasonably
                        possible.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    8. Your Rights
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Depending on your region, you may have rights to access, correct,
                    delete, restrict, object, port your data, withdraw consent, and opt
                    out of sale/share style processing. Contact:
                    <a
                        class="text-primary-600 hover:underline"
                        href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a
                    >.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    9. Children's Privacy
                </h2>
                <p>
                    The service is not directed to children under 13. If you believe a
                    child has provided personal data, contact us and we will review and act
                    promptly.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">10. Security</h2>
                <p>
                    We apply reasonable technical and organizational safeguards. No method
                    of transmission or storage is fully risk-free.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                    11. Account Deletion
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Use in-app deletion controls or visit
                    <a class="text-primary-600 hover:underline" href="/en/delete-account">
                        Delete Account
                    </a>
                    for a step-by-step process.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-3">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">12. Changes</h2>
                <p>
                    We may update this policy. Material updates are reflected with a new
                    date on this page.
                </p>
            </section>
        </article>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
